Christopher Nolan's latest upcoming movie is **The Odyssey**, set to release on July 17, 2026. This film is a grand adaptation of Homer's epic saga, following the Greek hero Odysseus on his challenging journey home after the Trojan War. The cast includes notable actors such as Matt Damon, Tom Holland, Anne Hathaway, and Zendaya, among others. The film promises to be a cinematic masterpiece, shot entirely on IMAX film, offering an immersive experience.